********************************************************************************
Requirements:
********************************************************************************

Following python packages are needed to run ygd:
BeautifulSoup
twill

To install them on Linux/UNIX:
   ( needs pip-python installed )
 $ pip-python install BeautifulSoup twill
   OR ( for Fedora )
 $ yum install python-BeautifulSoup python-twill


********************************************************************************
How to use the script?
********************************************************************************

 $ python ygd.py -u username -g group_name
 Password: ......

Thats it!
